                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For documentation relating to the convening by President Truman of a special
                    session of the Congress to deal with the problems of rising prices and the
                    economic crisis in western Europe, see <ref target="#pg_470">pages 470</ref> ff.
                    In an address broadcast on October 24 the President stated that the “most
                    imminent danger exists in France and in Italy”.</p>
            </div>
